enderite.description.autooffhand: Automatically puts stuff in your offhand.
enderite.description.flight: Allows you to jump infinite times with no delay.
enderite.description.jesus: Allows you to move through water fast.
enderite.description.nofall: Makes it so you cant take fall damage.
enderite.description.spider: Lets you crawl up walls like spiders.
enderite.description.tridentboost: Boosts your farther when using the trident.
enderite.description.vehiclefly: Allows you to jump infinite times with no delay in vehicles.
enderite.description.barrieresp: Lets you see barriers without holding the item.
enderite.description.fullbright: Lets you see in dark areas.
enderite.description.autofarm: Automatically places seeds and harvests sugar cane.
enderite.description.autofish: Automatically reel in the fishing rod and cast it.
enderite.description.fastmine: Allows you to break blocks faster.
